sata*       at atp?
#### IDE hard drives
wd*		at pciide? channel ? drive ? flags 0x0000

#### Pseudo devices
pseudo-device	loop	1	# network loopback

ide_cd* 	at pciide? channel ? drive ? flags 0x0001
